(15395, '_transient_hestia-update-response', 'O:8:"stdClass":13:{s:11:"new_version";s:6:"1.1.17";s:14:"stable_version";s:6:"1.1.17";s:4:"name";s:6:"Hestia";s:4:"slug";s:6:"hestia";s:3:"url";s:48:"https://themeisle.com/themes/hestia/?changelog=1";s:12:"last_updated";s:19:"2017-01-30 11:42:02";s:8:"homepage";s:36:"https://themeisle.com/themes/hestia/";s:7:"package";s:55:"http://downloads.themeisle.com/hestia/latest/hestia.zip";s:13:"download_link";s:55:"http://downloads.themeisle.com/hestia/latest/hestia.zip";s:8:"sections";a:2:{s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:9:"changelog";s:4406:"<p>v1.0.3 - 21/10/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with sections management</li>\n<li>Added style for the sidebar</li>\n<li>Small improvements in layout</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.4 - 24/10/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Improved sections order control</li>\n<li>Added hover effects on comments form/subscribe form</li>\n<li>Added show/hide controls for each section</li>\n<li>Allow html tags in the contact section</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.5 - 25/10/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update readme file</li>\n<li>Fixed WooCommerce issues</li>\n<li>Fixed section ordering on internal pages</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.6 - 28/10/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Improved colors options in customizer</li>\n<li>Compatibilty with the plugin YITH Woocommerce Zoom Magnifier</li>\n<li>Style attachment page</li>\n<li>Change default images ( compresed )</li>\n<li>Fixed responsive issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.7 - 18/11/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed footer widgets color</li>\n<li>Fixed sections order with WordPress 4.7</li>\n<li>Updated travis and fixed grunt errors</li>\n<li>Fixed theme check errors</li>\n<li>Display the content on frontpage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.8 - 24/11/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed layout for the cart button</li>\n<li>Fixed responsive issues</li>\n<li>Fixed themecheck errors</li>\n<li>Replaced screenshot</li>\n<li>Improved sticky posts style</li>\n<li>Improved contrast on frontpage sections</li>\n<li>Improved padding and margin issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.0.9 - 24/11/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed text colors in the Contact section</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.0 - 24/11/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed WooCommerce responsive issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.1 - 26/11/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed unnecessary .pot file</li>\n<li>Fixed data validation and sanitization issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.3 - 16/01/2017<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with submit button not centering on full width pages using Pirate Forms</li>\n<li>Added synchronized controls in the About section to allow customization</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with hover color for menu items</li>\n<li>Changed the way style.css is enqueued for child theme compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.4 - 25/01/2017<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use correct instructions for Sendinblue widget</li>\n<li>Changed slider speed from 400 seconds to 10 seconds</li>\n<li>Adjusted padding on menu items to match material kit pro</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.5 - 09/02/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make theme compatible with WPML and Polylang\n</li>\n<li>Improved Customize upsell layout</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.6 - 23/02/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Solved comment form issue.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.7 - 02/03/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with the sidebar position when only logged in users are able to posts comments\n</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with translations in the Pricing section</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.8 - 13/03/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Created Hestia Companion plugin for lite users\n</li>\n<li>Fixed pricing display issue on frontpage for WooCommerce products\n</li>\n<li>Fixed layout issues with ul and ol lists\n</li>\n<li>Added starter content for new users</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.9 - 13/03/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed default cases for frontpage sections controls</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.11 - 28/03/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed loading time issue in Mozilla Firefox\n</li>\n<li>Fixed small layout issues\n</li>\n<li>Refractor code\n</li>\n<li>Improved escaping</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.12 - 31/03/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed compatibility issue with Elementor page builder plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.13 - 05/04/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with shortcodes used in the About section causing Customizer to not load\n</li>\n<li>Fixed repeater using "file_get_contents" function.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.14 - 06/04/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed compatibility issues with WooCommerce 3.0.0\n</li>\n<li>Fixed issues with shortcodes and scripts entered in the About section</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.15 - 06/04/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed grund and fatal error when woocoommerce is not installed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.16 - 12/04/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Replaced screenshot\n</li>\n<li>Fixed thumbnails issues with WooCommerce 3.0.0\n</li>\n<li>Fixed jquery-ui dependency causing scripts not to load</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.1.17 - 21/04/2017 Changes: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update font-awesome library\n</li>\n<li>Allow HTML tags in the slider section and in the Big title section</li>\n</ul>\n";}s:7:"banners";s:41:"a:2:{s:4:"high";s:0:"";s:3:"low";s:0:"";}";s:6:"tested";s:5:"4.5.1";s:13:"compatibility";s:82:"a:1:{s:5:"4.5.1";a:1:{s:6:"1.5.15";a:3:{i:0;s:4:"100%";i:1;s:1:"5";i:2;s:1:"5";}}}";}', 'no'),
